    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虫巢在<strong>震怒</strong>。这颗星球已被<i>征服</i>。<i>今日，今日，就在今日</i>，它们向千万同族发出召唤。虫群<i>昂扬起来</i>，鞘翅摩擦出刺耳尖啸，甲壳迸裂声此起彼伏。<i>今日，今日，就在今日。</i>它们如洪流般奔涌，向着机械军团的营地倾泻。震荡着统一的战吼：<strong>杀无赦！杀无赦！杀无赦！</strong></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/ff28cd48f006ef8ca9f7580025fbdc5d.avif?t=1772276134\" width=614 height=60 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/9ed48293bd02ba97a6335c807b5860bf.poster.avif?t=1772276134\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/9ed48293bd02ba97a6335c807b5860bf.webm?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/9ed48293bd02ba97a6335c807b5860bf.mp4?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《<strong>虫群来袭</strong>》中，运营关乎存亡。必须采集足够多的资源、维持居民<i>温饱与士气值</i>。当<strong>虫群</strong>攻来时，确保防御<strong>一切就绪</strong>。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/f42047dd02fe0425040209955b7ac315.avif?t=1772276134\" width=614 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/60b5d69408129c9acef4a2965006f5f2.poster.avif?t=1772276134\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/60b5d69408129c9acef4a2965006f5f2.webm?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/60b5d69408129c9acef4a2965006f5f2.mp4?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由编组<i>你</i>的军团，训练军队对抗虫巢的<strong>最强大敌人</strong>。<strong>虫群</strong>的数量就是力量，攻击<strong>毫不留情</strong>。随时准备抗击<i>成千上万</i>的恶魔。 </p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/3acaf0521b5bea37f6f18bcf14b06ddd.avif?t=1772276134\" width=614 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/e35369f5ba393c1eb16c0f0b618779f4.poster.avif?t=1772276134\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/e35369f5ba393c1eb16c0f0b618779f4.webm?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/e35369f5ba393c1eb16c0f0b618779f4.mp4?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在众多<strong>神祇</strong>中选择一位，<i>他们的神圣力量</i>将助你踏上旅程。神的祝福会决定你的<strong>生死存亡</strong>。你可以选择投身于攻击、防御，还是探索<i>其他道路</i>？</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/37d75cce6e4bb68a8e29f152b50d92d5.avif?t=1772276134\" width=614 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/99593518b1718ae5929bd88a614e16ad.poster.avif?t=1772276134\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/99593518b1718ae5929bd88a614e16ad.webm?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/99593518b1718ae5929bd88a614e16ad.mp4?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>战斗</strong>中收集<strong>奥术精华</strong>，升级<strong>奥秘之书</strong>，解锁<strong>强大的技能</strong>，<i>彻底改变战局</i>。选择你的专属技能，打造你的<i>专属战斗方式</i>。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/1b1ab11f616b636e5abf0b6d5d53ff10.avif?t=1772276134\" width=614 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/8f0bf23ad215cbb6e2fd86f7a0e339ca.poster.avif?t=1772276134\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/8f0bf23ad215cbb6e2fd86f7a0e339ca.webm?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/8f0bf23ad215cbb6e2fd86f7a0e339ca.mp4?t=1772276134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入<strong>探险</strong>地图，<i>开启全新的旅程</i>。每次冒险都会有<strong>新的技能</strong>与<strong>强大的敌人</strong>，每局游戏都是独一无二的。你的每个决策都会<i>塑造</i>你的专属冒险之旅。</p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052730/extras/3640f8056b286b0f1dbfddb39d997254.avif?t=1772276134\" width=614 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别让时间耽误你！在关键时刻<strong>暂停</strong>游戏，做出<i>战术决策</i>。无论规划基地建设、指挥军队行动，或者泡杯热饮犒劳自己，你都值得拥有最佳体验。</p>",
